sentences.sentence: Four weeks later, another titi monkey came down with the same symptoms.
sentences.translation: 4周以后，另一个蒂蒂猴患同样的症状而病倒。

sentences.sentence: The titi is to the gamin what the moth is to the larva; the same being endowed with wings and soaring.
sentences.translation: titi对野孩来说，正如花蝴蝶之与幼虫，同是飞翔的生物。

sentences.sentence: Titi monkeys are one of the only species of primate that are monogamous, gibbons being one of the only other ones.
sentences.translation: 单配偶的灵长类动物只有两种，其中一种就是伶猴，另一种是长臂猿。
